<p id="notice"><%= notice %></p>

<h2 class="align-center blue">Resources for Wholesalers</h2>
<br>
<p>Browse the resources listed below to learn more about real estate wholesaling. <br>
  <br> Many of these experts have developed intense and well thought-out training programs inteded to coach anyone of any experience level into becoming a skilled real estate wholesaler. 
  Most training programs focus on the US as a whole, but if they are able to provide coaching for other areas of the country, they should say so in their profile. <br>
Many of the trainers below also have expanded into coaching investors on more than just wholesaling. Refer to their websites for full details.</p><br>

    <p class="align-right"><%= link_to new_resource_path, class: 'btn btn-info btn-md' do %>
      <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-pencil" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                New Resource
    <% end %></p>
  
        <% @resources.each do |resource| %>

        <%= link_to resource do %><!-- will make all resource clickable -->

          <div class="container listing-outline">

            <h3 class="black"><strong><%= resource.resource_name %></strong></h3>

            <h4><b class="blue">Specialties: </b><span class="black"><%= resource.specialties %></span></h4>

            <h4><b class="blue">Website: </b><span class="black"><%= resource.url %></span></h4>

            <% if user_signed_in? && current_user == resource.user %>

              <div class="align-right">

                <%= link_to edit_resource_path(resource), class: 'btn btn-info btn-sm' do %>
                    <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-wrench" aria-hidden="true"> Edit</span>
                <% end %>

                <%= link_to resource, method: :delete, data: { confirm: 'Are you sure?' }, class: 'btn btn-info btn-sm' do %>
                    <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-trash" aria-hidden="true"> Delete</span>
                <% end %>

              </div><!-- end align-right -->

            <% end %><!-- end if user signed in --> 
            
            <br>

            </div><!-- end .container .listing-outline -->
          

          <% end %><!-- end resource clickable link to itself -->
        <% end %><!-- end resources each do -->

    <br>

       <p class="align-right"><%= link_to new_resource_path, class: 'btn btn-info btn-md' do %>
      <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-pencil" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                New Resource
    <% end %></p>
  
    <div class="align-center"><p><%= will_paginate @resources, renderer: BootstrapPagination::Rails, class: 'align-center' %></p></div>


